      "description": "<span id=\"spandesc\"><p>This is a remote position.</p><p>Bookkeeper - Multi-Location Restaurant Group<br/></p><p>Schedule:<br/></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Part-time, 20 hours per week, Monday to Friday, 8 AM to 12 PM <br/></li>\n</ul><p>Client Timezone: CDT<br/></p><h4 id=\"m_-8207073541656986493client-overview\">Client Overview<br/></h4><p>Join a thriving multi-location restaurant group that’s revolutionizing the dining experience. This forward-thinking company is expanding rapidly, embracing cutting-edge technology and innovative management practices to stay ahead in the competitive food service industry.<br/></p><h4 id=\"m_-8207073541656986493job-description\">Job Description<br/></h4><p>As a Virtual Bookkeeper, you’ll be the financial backbone of this dynamic restaurant group. Using industry-specific software like Restaurant365, you’ll manage crucial financial operations across multiple locations. This role offers a unique blend of traditional accounting and modern restaurant management, providing you with invaluable experience in a growth-oriented environment. You’ll have the opportunity to directly impact the company’s success by providing accurate financial insights that drive strategic decisions.<br/></p><h4 id=\"m_-8207073541656986493responsibilities\">Responsibilities<br/></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Manage daily financial transactions using Restaurant365<br/></li>\n<li>Process invoices and handle accounts payable/receivable<br/></li>\n<li>Reconcile bank activities and match payments to invoices<br/></li>\n<li>Generate and analyze key financial reports (P&amp;amp;L, balance sheets, labor reports, COGS)<br/></li>\n<li>Prepare weekly financial reviews for management<br/></li>\n<li>Maintain meticulous financial records<br/></li>\n<li>Contribute to financial decision-making with timely, accurate data<br/></li>\n<li>Collaborate with the CFO and other team members to optimize financial processes<br/></li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n</span>\n<br/>\n<span id=\"spanreq\"><h3>Requirements</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Accounting degree<br/></li>\n<li>2-3 years bookkeeping experience, restaurant industry preferred<br/></li>\n<li>Strong grasp of accounting principles and financial management<br/></li>\n<li>Proficiency in accounting software, willingness to master Restaurant365<br/></li>\n<li>Exceptional attention to detail and commitment to accuracy<br/></li>\n<li>Sharp analytical and problem-solving skills<br/></li>\n<li>Self-motivated with excellent time management abilities<br/></li>\n<li>Fluent English with strong communication skills<br/></li>\n<li>Reliable internet connection for remote work<br/></li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n</span>\n<br/>",
