      "description": "<span id=\"spandesc\"><p>This is a remote position.</p><p>We are looking for a proactive and detail-oriented Data Analyst to join our team. This role will be part of the NA CDP Support Team / Braze Support and will focus on supporting business decisions through data-driven insights. The successful candidate will be responsible for data extraction, transformation, and comparison, as well as maintaining data pipelines and ensuring data quality.<br/></p><p><b>Job Activities</b><br/></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Perform <b>data extraction, transformation, and comparison</b> to support business decisions.<br/></li>\n<li>Collaborate with team members to build and maintain <b>data pipelines</b> for efficient data movement.<br/></li>\n<li>Identify anomalies and inconsistencies in data and systems, ensuring data quality.<br/></li>\n<li>Assist in troubleshooting data-related issues and implementing solutions.<br/></li>\n<li>Generate reports and visualizations to communicate insights effectively.<br/></li>\n<li>Support the optimization of existing processes to enhance operational efficiency.<br/></li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n</span>\n<br/>\n<span id=\"spanreq\"><h3>Requirements</h3><p><br/></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Proficiency in <b>SQL</b> for querying and analyzing data.<br/></li>\n<li>Basic understanding of <b>data analysis</b> and <b>visualization tools</b>.<br/></li>\n<li>Familiarity with <b>cloud environments</b> and their core concepts.<br/></li>\n<li>Foundational programming knowledge and a willingness to learn.<br/></li>\n<li>A <b>proactive</b> attitude with a desire to learn and grow.<br/></li>\n<li>Advanced proficiency in <b>English</b>, both written and spoken.<br/></li>\n</ul><p><b>Desirable</b><br/></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Exposure to <b>Microsoft Azure</b> or other cloud platforms.<br/></li>\n<li>Experience with <b>Python</b> for data manipulation and scripting.<br/></li>\n<li>Knowledge of tools like <b>Databricks</b> or other data processing platforms.<br/></li>\n<li>Familiarity with <b>Java</b> or similar programming languages.<br/></li>\n<li>Strong <b>teamwork</b> and collaboration skills.<br/></li>\n<li>Excellent <b>problem-solving</b> skills and attention to detail.<br/></li>\n<li>Ability to manage time effectively and prioritize tasks.<br/></li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n<b>Other Information</b>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<ul>\n<li><span><span>Remote job</span></span><br/></li>\n<li><span><span>Flexible work environment</span></span><br/></li>\n<li><span><span>Periodic feedback aiming at people development and career growth</span></span><br/></li>\n<li><span><span>Competitive Salary</span></span><br/></li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n</span>\n<br/>",
