      "description": "<span id=\"spandesc\"><p>This is a remote position.</p><p>We are looking for a proactive and detail-oriented <b>Data Engineer</b> to join our team. This role will focus on managing data flows, ensuring report structures are maintained, and guaranteeing that data is accurately processed and refreshed. The successful candidate will work with various tools and technologies such as <b>Power BI</b>, <b>Databricks</b>, <b>Python</b>, <b>Delta Lake</b>, and will take ownership of documentation and process improvements.<br/></p>\n<br/>\n<p><b>Job Activities</b><br/></p>\n<ul>\n<li><b>Take ownership of report structures</b>, ensuring quality and performance consistency across reports.<br/></li>\n<li><b>Create and monitor data flow</b>, ensuring seamless movement of data across systems and that it’s appropriately refreshed in reports.<br/></li>\n<li><b>Guarantee data refresh</b> in reports, ensuring timely and accurate data updates for business decision-making.<br/></li>\n<li>Keep <b>documentation updated</b>, using <b>SharePoint</b> to track requirements, processes, and solutions.<br/></li>\n<li>Work with cross-functional teams to <b>train and support</b> others in the use of data tools and platforms.<br/></li>\n<li><b>Collaborate</b> with business stakeholders to gather requirements and design efficient, scalable data pipelines and solutions.<br/></li>\n<li><b>Troubleshoot</b> and resolve any data-related issues, optimizing performance and ensuring data integrity.<br/></li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n</span>\n<br/>\n<span id=\"spanreq\"><h3>Requirements</h3><p><br/></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Experience with <b>Data Bricks</b> and <b>Data Warehousing</b>.<br/></li>\n<li>Strong proficiency in <b>Python (PySpark)</b> and <b>Delta Lake</b>.<br/></li>\n<li>Advanced knowledge of <b>Power BI</b>, with experience in creating dashboards and using <b>DAX</b> functions for data modeling and visualization.<br/></li>\n<li>Knowledge of <b>NoSQL</b> and <b>ETL</b> processes.<br/></li>\n<li>Ability to handle <b>large volumes of data</b> and create <b>optimized</b> data models.<br/></li>\n<li>Ability to <b>take ownership</b> of the report structure and ensure alignment with business goals.<br/></li>\n<li>Strong <b>English communication</b> skills to effectively <b>collect requirements</b> from clients and collaborate with international teams.<br/></li>\n<li>Highly <b>organized</b> with strong attention to detail in managing data, documentation, and reporting.<br/></li>\n<li>Experience in creating <b>documentation</b> in SharePoint, keeping requirements and solutions clearly recorded.<br/></li>\n<li>Ability to <b>train other people</b>, with a focus on transferring knowledge and ensuring the team's success.<br/></li>\n<li><span>Advanced English<br/></span></li>\n</ul><p><b>Desirable</b><br/></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Familiarity with <b>Azure</b> or other cloud platforms.<br/></li>\n<li>Experience with <b>Tableau</b> for data visualization.<br/></li>\n</ul>\n<b>Other Information</b>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<ul>\n<li><span><span>Remote job</span></span><br/></li>\n<li><span><span>Flexible work environment</span></span><br/></li>\n<li><span><span>Periodic feedback aiming at people development and career growth</span></span><br/></li>\n<li><span><span>Competitive Salary</span></span><br/></li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n</span>\n<br/>",
